    <p><b>Maytag (dependability)</b> — MGR / MER families, 10-year limited warranty positioning. See <a href="/brands/maytag-stove-repair/">Maytag stove repair</a>.</p>
    <p><b>Amana (value)</b> — AGR / AER families, value-tier. See <a href="/brands/amana-range-repair/">Amana range repair</a>.</p>
    <p><b>KitchenAid (premium)</b> — premium sub-brand, typically range-configuration focus. See <a href="/brands/kitchenaid-cooktop-repair/">KitchenAid cooktop repair</a>.</p>
