    </table>
    <p class="small">Related: <a href="/brands/whirlpool-range-repair/">Whirlpool range repair</a> · <a href="/brands/maytag-stove-repair/">Maytag stove repair (Whirlpool family)</a> · <a href="/brands/amana-range-repair/">Amana range repair</a>.</p>
