  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>LA service areas — where our Whirlpool stove calls come from</h2>
    <div class="area-grid">
      <div><h4>San Fernando Valley rental + mid-market</h4><p>Panorama City · North Hills · Van Nuys · Reseda · Sherman Oaks · Northridge</p></div>
